Analiza

ggplot(bank)+
  geom_histogram(aes(age), binwidth=1)+
  labs(title = "Rozkad wieku")+
  theme_bw()

ggplot(bank, aes(x=age, fill=education))+
  geom_density(alpha=0.4)+
  labs(title = "Zalenosc wieku, statusu i edukacji")+
  facet_wrap(~marital)

ggplot(bank, aes(y=age, x = loan))+
  geom_violin()+
  labs(title = "Zalenosc wieku, statusu i poyczki")+
  facet_wrap(~marital)

ggplot(bank, aes(age, balance))+
  geom_point() +
  geom_smooth(method="lm", color="red", se=FALSE) +
  labs(title = "Zaleno wieku i balance")
